OL,3,CHate crime victims left vulnerable and
OL,4,Cscared in wake of riots
OL,6,FVulnerable and scared: Violence over
OL,7,Fthe past week has destroyed properties
OL,8,Fand fuelled disorder, but the
OL,9,Femotional and mental toll is still
OL,10,Fbeing counted
OL,12,FViolence over the past week has
OL,13,Fdamaged businesses and properties, but
OL,14,Fit is the hate crimes that have left
OL,15,Fpeople from diverse backgrounds
OL,16,Ffeeling vulnerable and scared.
