OL,3,CHate crime victims left vulnerable and
OL,4,Cscared in wake of riots
OL,6,FThe rioters may have departed but the
OL,7,Fscars from the disorder and violence
OL,8,Fthey have brought remain. Victims of
OL,9,Fhate crimes are trying, but struggling
OL,10,Fto tape over the cracks.
OL,12,FIn Middlesbrough, homes and vehicles
OL,13,Fwere targeted by far-right rioters.
OL,14,FPooja, who moved from India to the
OL,15,Fnorth of England, met the gaze of
OL,16,Frioters through her window.
OL,18,F"I was looking out my window and I saw
OL,19,Fthe hate in their eyes," she told ITV
OL,20,FNews.
