OL,3,CHate crime victims left vulnerable and
OL,4,Cscared in wake of riots
OL,6,FThey trashed her car and tried to
OL,7,Fbreak into her home.
OL,9,FShe added: "I thought I was coming to
OL,10,Fa country that respects all people and
OL,11,Fbeing a part of it, but after this,
OL,12,Fthis changed my mind. I don't think
OL,13,FI'm going to continue living here.
OL,15,F"I was scared of ghosts but I'm scared
OL,16,Fof people now."
OL,18,FThe community came together to clear
OL,19,Fthe physical remnants of disorder -
OL,20,Fthe attitudes of some seemingly still
OL,21,Fremain.
