OL,3,CHate crime victims left vulnerable and
OL,4,Cscared in wake of riots
OL,6,FIn Burnley, the hate was not reserved
OL,7,Ffor the living.
OL,9,FGraves were daubed in paint,
OL,10,Fheadstones were defaced, with one man
OL,11,Fspeaking of his devastation after
OL,12,F"evil individuals" desecrated his
OL,13,Fyounger brother's grave.
OL,15,FSuweb Ali told ITV News: "We feel like
OL,16,Fwe couldn't protect him alive and now
OL,17,Fhe should be at rest and peace."
