OL,3,CHate crime victims left vulnerable and
OL,4,Cscared in wake of riots
OL,6,FThe local community has since worked
OL,7,Fto remove the paint poured on the
OL,8,Fheadstones, but Suweb says the
OL,9,Fincident has frightened his family.
OL,11,F"We're all scared," he said. "I've
OL,12,Fcancelled summer plans with my
OL,13,Fchildren.
OL,15,F"Everyone wants the same: to live
OL,16,Fequally. But we're going back in time."
OL,18,FLancashire Police said it was treating
OL,19,Fthe hate crime "incredibly seriously".
