OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "We have launched
OL,7,Fan investigation after a report of
OL,8,Fcriminal damage in Burnley today
OL,9,F(Monday, August 5).
OL,11,F"We were called around 4:15pm to
OL,12,FBurnley Cemetery on Rossendale Road
OL,13,Fafter a report that paint had been
OL,14,Fpoured across headstones in a Muslim
OL,15,Fburial area.
OL,17,F"The investigation into this matter is
OL,18,Fvery much ongoing. We are taking this
OL,19,Fmatter incredibly seriously and this
OL,20,Fis being treated as a hate crime.
